Agathe de La Fontaine https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Agathe_de_La_Fontaine 0 Agathe de La Fontaine (born 27 March 1972) is a French actress. Her film roles include Train de vie (1998), which shared the 1999 Sundance World Cinema Audience Award with Run Lola Run, and Love in Paris, the sequel to 9½ Weeks. La Fontaine was married to former football player Emmanuel Petit. Agathe_de_La_Fontaine ( born 27_March_1972 ) is a_French_actress .
